[{'type': 'text/html', 'language': None, 'base': 'https://www.upwork.com/ab/feed/jobs/rss?q=scraping', 'value': 'Sorare is a Fantasy Football game released in 2019 where you collect digital cards (NFT) bearing the image of football players.

The game is based on Ethereum technology in which its own marketplace is integrated. The API is in Opensource made available by GraphQL.

Objectives:
- Create an Autobuyer bot which, based on a given average price, would be able to buy a card as soon as it is put on the market. Provided that it is X% lower than its average price, it is a question here of spotting a price error and buying it as quickly as possible, before the other bots in service on the platform.

For Example:

-If the newPlayer1 on the market is 20% cheaper then the average price, fast automated buy.
- After that more attributes: Only Players from 18-35 years old or only from European Leagues. etc.

- Hide IP and ways to not be blocked.

You can find some information here:
https://github.com/sorare

The game is this:
sorare.com
